headline: Howmet Aerospace (HWM) Fell as It Missed Earnings Expectations
summary: Janus Henderson Investors, an investment management company, released its “Janus Henderson Forty Fund” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The fund returned 19.34% in the second quarter, compared to the Russell 1000 Growth Index’s 17.84% return.
